To render the particles on the canvas, we can create an array of particle objects and loop through them, calling the "draw" method for each one:

```js
let canvas = document.getElementById("particle-canvas");
let ctx = canvas.getContext("2d");

let particles = [];

for (let i = 0; i < 100; i++) {
  particles.push(createParticle(
    Math.random() * canvas.width,
